All Classes

Class Summary
Class Description
Book
A Book is a child object of a Publication so it inherits its methods and variables.
BookChapter
A BookChapter is a child class of the Book class (which is a child class of the Publication class) so it inherits their methods and variables.
CISUC
A CISUC class represents an institution that contains research groups, researchers and publications.
CisucManager
A CisucManager class is where the program starts.
ConferenceArticle
A ConferenceArticle is a child class of a Publication class so it inherits its methods and variables.
ConferenceArticleBook
A ConferenceArticleBook is a child class of the Book class (which is a child class of the Publication class) so it inherits their methods and variables.
Date
The Date class represents a real life date.
EffectiveMember
A EffectiveMember class is a child from the Researcher class.
MagazineArticle
A MagazineArticle is a child class of a Publication class so it inherits its methods and variables.
Publication
A Publication is an abstract class that represents a publication made by a researcher or a group of researchers.
Researcher
The Researcher class represents a researcher that is part of a ResearchGroup and that works in a CISUC object.
ResearchGroup
The ResearchGroup class represents a group of Researchers that work on a same topic in the CISUC institution.
Student
A Student class is a child from the Researcher class.
